header.gameNote: OHIO VALLEY CONFERENCE MEN'S TOURNAMENT - FINAL

videos.description: A heavily guarded Ja Morant fights in the paint to create space and make a layup.
videos.headline: Murray State's Morant drains heavily contested layup

videos.description: Byron Hawkins drives to the basket and is fouled while shooting for an and-1.
videos.headline: Murray State's Hawkins fired up after and-1

videos.description: Terry Miller Jr. no-look passes to Brion Sanchious who takes it to the rim for an emphatic flush.
videos.headline: Murray State dropping dimes like it's hot

videos.description: The Racers defeat the Bruins 68-51 to become the Ohio Valley Conference Champions and clinch the 16th NCAA Tournament berth.
videos.headline: Murray State celebrates winning OVC tournament
